# Localization Guide

## Supported Languages

The app supports the following languages:
- English (en-US)
- Japanese (ja)
- German (de-DE)
- Spanish (es-ES)
- French (fr-FR)
- Italian (it)
- Korean (ko)
- Thai (th)
- Turkish (tr)
- Vietnamese (vi)

## Key Files
- [locate/Localizable.xcstrings](mdc:locate/Localizable.xcstrings): Contains all localized strings
- [fastlane/metadata](mdc:fastlane/metadata): Contains app store metadata for each language

## String Categories
- UI Elements
- Error Messages
- Subscription Messages
- Analytics Events
- Feature Names

## Adding New Strings
1. Add the string to [locate/Localizable.xcstrings](mdc:locate/Localizable.xcstrings)
2. Provide translations for all supported languages
3. Use descriptive keys that reflect the string's purpose
4. Group related strings together (e.g., all subscription-related strings)
